{
  "texts": [
    "The 1975 respondents took, on average, 12.2 min to complete the questionnaire (SD: 6.9 min, median: 10.4 min).",
    "The respondents resided in 34 different countries.",
    "The country for 5 respondents was unknown.",
    "The five most highly represented countries were South Africa (n = 517), the UK (n = 409), Portugal (n = 259), Poland (n = 216), and Italy (n = 115).The responses to the general questions are shown in Table 3.",
    "The mean age of respondents was 32.0 years (SD: 10.8) (G1), and the sample comprised nearly equal numbers of males and females (G2)."
  ]
}